{"tid":2014851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局通知港台9月收回廣播道教育電視中心！","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:29:34.000Z","uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"874196e66e1a541b34b6aba039d44bc16fb48dd8","tid":2014851,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f156b8314c7df5c3a33fe939afe7a06394d7b4","tid":2014851,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rfg0wC7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfg0wC7.png&h=487283a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a33f9125beb17568af886528ab6467abe6ba325","tid":2014851,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:28:28.000Z","msg":"消息指教育局將收回教育電視中心<br />\n13.05.2020 17:24<br />\n<br />\n消息指，教育局決定9月收回位於廣播道的教育電視中心，港台已通知員工傍晚開會。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員<span style=\"color: gold;\">葛珮帆</span>表示，審計報告早前已揭示教育電視收視偏低，製作少，而且慢，她認為教育電視已完成歷史任務，隨著政府將教育電視製作費削減至零，收回中心也是順理成章，她希望教育局思考如何更具成本效益，製作更吸引和互動的教材，亦希望港台能妥善處理百多名受影響員工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287272&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287272%26csid%3D261_367&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=984bbe12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287272&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"dc5da8373dcae7757e5e7f5b36313301e89db094","tid":2014851,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"政治打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}